markets.question: Formula 1: Which team will collect more points at the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix, Mercedes or Ferrari?
markets.description:
The 2022 Belgian Grand Prix is a Formula 1 event scheduled to take place over 44 laps of the 7.004-kilometre Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps on Sunday, August 28.

This is a market on whether Mercedes or Ferrari will collect more points at the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix.

Constructor teams are awarded the same points won by the drivers who race in their cars. If, for example, the drivers earn 25 and 18 points, respectively, their constructor team will be awarded 43 points, which are the points won by both drivers combined.

This market will resolve to “Mercedes” if Mercedes collects more points than Ferrari at the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix. This market will resolve to “Ferrari” if Ferrari collects more points than Mercedes at the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix. If both teams collect the same number of points, this market will resolve 50-50.

If for any reason the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix is rescheduled to a different time and date on or before September 4, 2022, the same market conditions will apply. If the race is rescheduled to a time and date after September 4, 2022, this market will resolve to 50-50.

markets.question: Formula 1: Will 17 or more drivers complete the 2022 Belgian Grand Prix?
markets.description:
